Notes: Stout sent game to overtime on Hendricks' layup at the buzzer after SP's
Houghton hit two free throws with four seconds left...After SP scored first
four points of OT, Stout closed game with 13-1 run, taking first lead since
5:46 mark of first half...SP led by as many as 14 points with 9:43 left.
Game.Officials: Wayne Brevik,  Bernie Barribeau,  Dennis Inderdahl
